    "display_name": "Typography Challenge",
    "long_instructions": "#Typography Challenge\r\n\r\nWith the help of AI, improve the page's typography so it's consistent. This can include:\r\n   - Heading hierarchy - clear difference between title, section heads, subheads\r\n   - Body readability - comfortable size, line height, line length, spacing\r\n   - Emphasis elements - links, quotes, lists, captions\r\n   \r\n::: details [Example AI Style Prompts]\r\nTry having AI update the typography with these example prompts:\r\n- *Style the title to be larger and uppercase. Make it visually distinct from the sub-titles.*\r\n- *Style the body text with 1.5 line height and comfortable max-width.*\r\n- *Improve the blockquote with larger size left border, and italics for emphasis.*\r\n:::",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Improve the web page's typography so it is consistent.",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://images.code.org/d896757c80f2e8a64c1d60168c278ce0-typography.png",
    "start_sources": {
      "folders": {
      },
      "files": {
        "1": {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "index.html",
          "language": "html",
          "contents": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>The Pulse — Article</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <a class=\"skip-link\" href=\"#main\">Skip to content</a>\n\n  <header class=\"site-header\">\n    <div class=\"container header-inner\">\n      <a class=\"brand\" href=\"#home\">The <strong>Pulse</strong></a>\n      <nav aria-label=\"Primary\">\n        <ul class=\"nav\">\n          <li><a href=\"#tech\">Tech</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#culture\">Culture</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#opinion\">Opinion</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"main\">\n    <article class=\"article container\">\n      <header class=\"article-meta\">\n        <h1 class=\"article-title\">Student projects are getting smarter</h1>\n        <p class=\"byline\">By <a href=\"#author\">Ari Johnson</a> • March 8, 2025</p>\n      </header>\n\n      <figure class=\"hero-media\">\n        <img src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/mag/1200/680\" alt=\"Students collaborating on laptops\" />\n        <figcaption>Robotics, media arts, and coding clubs are teaming up.</figcaption>\n      </figure>\n\n      <div class=\"content\">\n        <p>Across schools this year, clubs are sharing resources and tools to ship bigger ideas. From organizing makerspaces to publishing digital magazines, teams are discovering new ways to collaborate.</p>\n\n        <h2 class=\"section-head\">Less chaos, more flow</h2>\n        <p>Groups that once kept notes in five places are moving to shared hubs. It’s easier to see what’s next and who needs help.</p>\n        <p>When teammates can follow a single plan, they spend less time searching and more time building.</p>\n\n        <blockquote>\n          “We finished a week early once we kept tasks, files, and chat in one place.”\n        </blockquote>\n\n        <h3 class=\"subhead\">What students are trying</h3>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Checklists for weekly builds</li>\n          <li>Templates for project plans</li>\n          <li>Short retros to reduce blockers</li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <p>Want to see more examples? Visit our <a href=\"#guide\">guide</a> for stories and starter kits collected from clubs around the district.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <aside class=\"related\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-head\">Related reading</h2>\n        <ul class=\"related-list\">\n          <li><a href=\"#1\">How to run a 20-minute retrospective</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#2\">Designing for accessibility from day one</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"#3\">Publishing your club’s digital zine</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </aside>\n    </article>\n\n    <footer class=\"site-footer container\">\n      <p>© 2025 The Pulse Magazine</p>\n    </footer>\n  </main>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
          "active": true,
          "folderId": "0"
        },
        "2": {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "styles.css",
          "language": "css",
          "contents": "/* =========================================\n   Make hierarchy + readability better.\n   ========================================= */\n\n/* Tokens */\n:root{\n  --accent: #2563eb;\n  --text: #1f2937;\n  --muted: #6b7280;\n  --surface: #ffffff;\n  --bg: #f6f7fb;\n  --border: #e5e7eb;\n\n  /* POLISH TARGET: create a type scale (xs/sm/base/lg/xl/2xl…) */\n}\n\n/* Base */\n*{ box-sizing: border-box; }\nhtml, body { margin:0; padding:0; }\nbody{\n  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;\n  color: var(--text);\n  background: var(--bg);\n  line-height: 1.35; /* POLISH TARGET: too tight for body text */\n}\nimg{ max-width:100%; display:block; }\na{ color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; } /* POLISH TARGET: add underline on hover */\nh1,h2,h3{ margin: 0 0 8px 0; line-height: 1.15; } /* sizes below are too close together */\np{ margin: 0 0 10px 0; } /* inconsistent rhythm */\n\n/* Skip link */\n.skip-link{ position:absolute; left:-9999px; top:auto; }\n.skip-link:focus{ left:16px; top:16px; background:#000; color:#fff; padding:8px 12px; }\n\n/* Layout */\n.container{\n  width: 1000px;           /* POLISH TARGET: fixed width */\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 0 10px;\n}\n.site-header{\n  background: var(--surface);\n  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n}\n.header-inner{\n  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;\n  padding: 12px 0;\n}\n.brand{ text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); font-weight: 800; }\n.nav{ display:flex; gap: 16px; list-style:none; margin:0; padding:0; }\n.nav a{ color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }\n\n/* Article */\n.article{ padding: 20px 0 30px; }\n.article-title{\n  font-size: 28px;  /* POLISH TARGET: not strong enough vs h2 */\n  font-weight: 700; /* consider uppercase/letter-spacing */\n  text-transform: none;\n  margin-top: 12px;\n}\n.byline{ color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; }\n\n.hero-media{ margin: 12px 0 16px; }\n.hero-media img{ border-radius: 10px; }\n.hero-media figcaption{\n  font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); /* POLISH TARGET: consider tighter leading and spacing */\n}\n\n.content{\n  /* POLISH TARGETS:\n     - No max-width → lines are very long (hard to read)\n     - Line-height is tight (uses body default)\n     - Paragraph spacing is inconsistent\n  */\n}\n\n.section-head{              /* h2 */\n  font-size: 22px;          /* too close to h1; needs accent color/spacing */\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: var(--text);\n  margin: 16px 0 8px;\n}\n.subhead{                   /* h3 */\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: var(--text);       /* no visual distinction from body */\n  margin: 12px 0 6px;\n}\n\nblockquote{\n  margin: 12px 0;\n  padding: 8px 10px;\n  border-left: 3px solid #cbd5e1; /* faint; no italics */\n  color: #374151;\n  /* POLISH TARGET: style for emphasis (size, line-height, font-style) */\n}\n\nul{\n  margin: 8px 0 12px 18px;   /* meh spacing; cramped */\n  padding: 0;\n}\nul li{ margin: 6px 0; }      /* POLISH TARGET: improve list readability */\n\n.related{\n  margin-top: 20px;\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding-top: 14px;\n}\n.related-list{\n  margin: 8px 0 0 16px; padding:0;\n}\n.related-list a{ text-decoration: none; } /* POLISH TARGET: add hover/underline */\n\n.site-footer{\n  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);\n  padding: 16px 0;\n  text-align: center;\n  color: var(--muted);\n}\n\n/* Responsive (POLISH TARGET: minimal) */\n@media (max-width: 700px){\n  .container{ width: 92%; } /* still a bit wide; refine if needed */\n}\n",
          "folderId": "0",
          "active": false
        }
